keyPolicies.policyDescription: The leaflet mentions improving the local environment by cleaning up parks, addressing air quality and tackling litter.
A fair parking policy is stated as a goal, particularly to improve the situation around Peckham Rye station.

mentions.candidate: Lally Palmer is dedicated to Peckham & Rye Lane and routinely consults with residents on local issues.
mentions.tacticalSituation: The leaflet urges tactical consideration, noting it's only Labour that can beat the Conservatives in Peckham & Rye Lane.

issues.environment: Mentions improving the local environment including parks, air quality and tackling litter.

housing.content: Fair parking policy around Peckham Rye station

leaflet.personalStatement: Lally Palmer is mentioned as working hard for residents, with a record of action and a promise for more.

images.caption: Lally Palmer with a local resident and a child in a park.
